Rent from a 5-STAR host that has over a DECADE of experience and will get you a quality vehicle!
I have been car sharing for over 10 years now and know how important a clean and well serviced car is. Book from a host that knows what they are doing.

NOHO CARS NOW

Hey, my name's Harron. I was born in Manila, Philippines and immigrated to Hawaii. i joined the Air Force which allowed me to satiate my wanderlust. I've been to every state and Puerto Rico and have traveled to 38 countries so far. I've lived in AZ, VA, and DC. I've settled down in Portland, OR since 2017.
I also love cars and enjoy meeting people so Turo sounds like a great idea to me :)
Active person in community and working towards making Portland Oregon an enjoyable and fun place to come too.

Welcome to Eazy Car Rental, your trusted choice for convenient and reliable vehicle rentals in the vibrant city of Portland, Oregon. Embracing the spirit of the Pacific Northwest, Eazy Car Rental combines ease of service with a commitment to customer satisfaction.

Marine Corps veteran and a full time father.  I hold myself to a high standard when conducting any business.  You can definitely count on me to take care of your trips.

Our goal is to make sure people visiting Oregon will have a memorable and enjoyable time.  We provide camping and camping supplies, along with rooftop tents and other things for outdoor activities.

We are currently working on locations for airbnb rentals.  Follow us we will have some places in the near future.

I’m very a responsible mom & business owner. I enjoy vacationing in Maui with my family. My hobbies include housework & yard work. 😂 I’m pretty busy on most days! I’m curious about Turo. We will see where it goes…

Hi I’m Jacob, I am a Portland native and happy to help y’all find your way around town! My goal is 5 star service and to be accommodating as possible! Feel free to contact me anytime if there’s anything I can help with!

Hi! My name is Mingali, and I hope you will enjoy, love,
and care for our family's electric vehicles like we do!
We do our best to provide great service and communication to ensure you an excellent vehicle and rental experience.
Hey guys! My Fiance is a Power Host and he finally convinced me to list my Prius. So here it is. Thanks for stopping by!
